description: Russia has reported more than 220,000 cases of the virus, the third highest tally worldwide.
title: Coronavirus: Putin eases Russian lockdown as cases rise
title_page: Coronavirus: Putin eases Russian lockdown as cases rise - BBC News
maintext: That means Russia now has more confirmed cases than both Italy and the UK. Only Spain and the US have reported more infections. However, comparisons between countries are not always accurate because of different factors such as the extent of their testing.
